Combining both MOI datasets into one dataset
```{r}
mois <- rbind(MOI1, MOI46, MOI15)


mois <- na.omit(mois)

mois$dil.log <- log10(mois$dilution)
mois$moi.log <- log10(mois$MOI)


## write.csv(mois, here("MOI/data/20251113_CombinedMOI.csv"))

mois.group <- mois %>% group_by(virus, moi.log) %>%
  summarise(norm.avg = mean(norm))

```

